<h4><a href="https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/pEyk751J31Y-FlZuHL6t6w">国行 Nintendo Switch 正式支持腾讯视频</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1376873" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/img16.jpg" alt="" width="1280" height="853" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/img16.jpg 1280w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/img16-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/img16-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/img16-1024x682.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px" /></p>
<p>昨天，腾讯视频（体验版）正式上线 Nintendo e 商店，意味着国行用户可在 Nintendo Switch 上使用腾讯视频，并支持「掌上模式」「桌面模式」和「电视模式」三种观看模式。</p>
<p>目前，该版腾讯视频包含电视剧、电影、综艺、动漫、少儿和纪录片 6 大频道，视频内容最高支持 1080P 画面清晰度。</p>
<h3><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1293889" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/dagongs.png" alt="" width="1029" height="180" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/dagongs.png 1029w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/dagongs-360x63.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/dagongs-768x134.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/dagongs-1024x179.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1029px) 100vw, 1029px" /></h3>
<h4><a href="https://www.cnbeta.com/articles/tech/1049367.htm">Facebook 和 Instagram 警告美国用户总统大选仍在进行中</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1376874" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/f2feb3709cd9b8e.jpeg" alt="" width="700" height="642" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/f2feb3709cd9b8e.jpeg 700w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/f2feb3709cd9b8e-360x330.jpeg 360w" sizes="(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px" /></p>
<p>cnBeta 消息，Facebook 和 Instagram 均在应用中加入弹窗告示美国用户「选票正在计算中」，并引导用户访问应用内其它选举相关信息。</p>
<p>在这个通知上，两款应用还增加了时间戳，以更精确地显示通知时效性。昨天，特朗普在所有选票统计完成前过早地宣称自己已经获胜。</p>
<h4><a href="https://finance.sina.com.cn/tech/2020-11-04/doc-iiznctkc9514991.shtml">饿了么外卖可送到大兴机场登机口</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1376875" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/0lMrdweU4rA.jpeg" alt="" width="1271" height="847" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/0lMrdweU4rA.jpeg 1271w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/0lMrdweU4rA-360x240.jpeg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/0lMrdweU4rA-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/0lMrdweU4rA-1024x682.jpeg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1271px) 100vw, 1271px" /></p>
<p>TechWeb 消息，北京大兴国际机场和饿了么合作，开启外送服务。</p>
<p>旅客可通过大兴机场 app 或饿了么 app，让骑手将餐配送到登机口。基于机场环境的特殊性，消费者在机场下单购买的餐食将在 30 分钟内送达登机口。</p>
<p>为了适应机场内部环境，饿了么机场的「特别配送队」研发了专属的配送箱，箱子类似行李箱。</p>
<p>目前，大兴机场外卖项目上线产品涵盖 21 家餐饮品牌，近 700 款餐品，涉及中式正餐、中式快餐、咖啡茶饮、日料轻食、烘焙甜品等餐饮品类。</p>
<h4><a href="https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2020-11-04/california-projected-to-side-with-gig-economy-on-labor-issue">加州选民投票通过「22 号提案」，网约车司机将不归为雇员</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1376876" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/GettyImages-1219237615.jpg" alt="" width="1200" height="675" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/GettyImages-1219237615.jpg 1200w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/GettyImages-1219237615-360x203.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/GettyImages-1219237615-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/GettyImages-1219237615-1024x576.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></p>
<p>彭博社消息，加州选民投票通过了「22 号提案（Proposition 22）」，这意味着 Uber、Lyft 司机等其它零工经济工作人员不会被视作平台的正式雇员，而是独立合同工。</p>
<p>他们将获得部分企业福利，但并不能享受完整的正式员工福利。有统计预测，Uber 和 Lyft 一年会因此节省超过一亿美元的成本。</p>
<p>周三美股收盘，打车应用 Uber 和 Lyft 双双大幅收涨，Uber 涨 14.61%，Lyft 涨 11.28%。</p>
<h4><a href="https://finance.sina.com.cn/tech/2020-11-04/doc-iiznezxr9900826.shtml">盒马火锅正式上线盒马和饿了么</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1376877" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/eda9-kcieywa3144290.jpg" alt="" width="550" height="411" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/eda9-kcieywa3144290.jpg 550w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/eda9-kcieywa3144290-360x269.jpg 360w" sizes="(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px" /></p>
<p>新浪消息，盒马昨天正式在全国盒马和饿了么上线发售盒马火锅。官方宣称，盒马火锅锅底数量多达 40 多种，食材种类超 2000 个，价格约为火锅店的一半。</p>
<p>盒马 3R 事业部总经理宁强表示，相信火锅的外卖占比未来能够超过一半，而盒马火锅也将被视为今冬第一大品，盒马对火锅的投入将不设上限。</p>
<h4><a href="https://36kr.com/newsflashes/953477148883332">字节跳动员工人数将突破 10 万人</a></h4>
<p>36kr 消息，字节跳动今年在国内招聘员工总数已接近 3 万人，并计划在年底前再开放 1 万个工作岗位，届时，其员工总数将突破 10 万人。</p>
<h3><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1357461" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/citylife.png" alt="" width="1029" height="153" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/citylife.png 1029w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/citylife-360x54.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/citylife-768x114.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/citylife-1024x152.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1029px) 100vw, 1029px" /></h3>
<h4><a href="https://weibo.com/6115560351/Jslr6c67E?from=page_1002066115560351_profile&amp;wvr=6&amp;mod=weibotime&amp;type=comment#_rnd1604477989220">上海国际旅游度假区接待游客量恢复至去年 80%</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1376878" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/OCR-L-DISNEY-SHANGHAI-0512-07.jpg" alt="" width="780" height="519" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/OCR-L-DISNEY-SHANGHAI-0512-07.jpg 780w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/OCR-L-DISNEY-SHANGHAI-0512-07-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/OCR-L-DISNEY-SHANGHAI-0512-07-768x511.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 780px) 100vw, 780px" /></p>
<p>国是直通车消息，今年上海国际旅游度假区预计接待游客 1400 万人次，恢复到去年的 80%。</p>
<p>​上海迪士尼乐园于 5 月 11 日重新开园，其复工复产的做法，也成为全球迪士尼主题乐园行业重新开放、常态化条件下运营管理的标杆。</p>
<h4><a href="https://variety.com/2020/music/news/grammy-awards-change-world-music-to-global-1234821922/">格莱美「最佳世界音乐专辑奖」更名</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1376879" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/grammy_awards_logo.jpg" alt="" width="1200" height="675" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/grammy_awards_logo.jpg 1200w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/grammy_awards_logo-360x203.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/grammy_awards_logo-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/grammy_awards_logo-1024x576.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></p>
<p>《Variety》消息，（美国）国家录音艺术科学学院宣布，正式将格莱美奖中的「World Music Album（世界音乐专辑）」奖项更名为「Global Music Album（全球音乐专辑）」。</p>
<p>据悉，该改变是音乐人、民族音乐学家和语言学家共同讨论的结果，旨在剔除原本奖项名中指向的「殖民主义、民俗和 ‘非美国的’」含义，以更好地适应该奖项代表的多样性和文化趋势。</p>
<h4><a href="https://luxe.co/post/125945">耐克将总部裁员人数增至 700 人</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1376880" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/153654789188719431.jpg" alt="" width="1000" height="563" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/153654789188719431.jpg 1000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/153654789188719431-360x203.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/153654789188719431-768x432.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" /></p>
<p>华丽志消息，耐克调整了其全球总部的裁员计划，裁员人数从 7 月宣布的 500 人增加到 700 人。</p>
<p>据悉，被裁员工中包括了全球总部育儿中心的 192 名工作人员。耐克将改变育儿支持策略，并在总部以外的地区推出育儿福利，将育儿机会扩大到包括零售和分销工作人员在内的数千名员工。</p>
<h3><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1293890" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo.png" alt="" width="1029" height="180" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo.png 1029w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo-360x63.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo-768x134.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo-1024x179.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1029px) 100vw, 1029px" /></h3>
<h4><a href="https://s.weibo.com/weibo?q=%23%E4%B8%89%E5%A4%A7%E8%BF%90%E8%90%A5%E5%95%86%E5%9B%9E%E5%BA%945G%E5%A5%97%E9%A4%90%E6%97%A0%E6%B3%95%E6%94%B94G%23&amp;Refer=top">运营商回应 5G 套餐无法改 4G</a></h4>
<p>近期，5G 套餐成为各大运营商首推的产品，有网友反馈，在运营商的 app 上，4G 套餐办理入口消失。深报视听记者实地采访发现，想从 5G 套餐改回 4G 套餐，只能到线下营业厅申请操作。</p>
<p>网友：「升级虽是趋势，但只要 4G 还存在，就应该由消费者选择用。」「日夜推销 5G 套餐就算了，还把 4G 的速度降得那么慢就过分了。」</p>
<h3><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1357582" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/thur.png" alt="" width="1029" height="153" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/thur.png 1029w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/thur-360x54.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/thur-768x114.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/thur-1024x152.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1029px) 100vw, 1029px" /></h3>
<h4><a href="https://www.archdaily.cn/cn/949512/orstedhua-yuan-gong-yu-qi-fu-die-jia-li-mian-yang-tai-tegnestuen-lokal">Ørsted 花园公寓 @ 丹麦</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1375954" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/HAMPUS-Feature_Image-1.jpg" alt="" width="1200" height="893" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/HAMPUS-Feature_Image-1.jpg 1200w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/HAMPUS-Feature_Image-1-360x268.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/HAMPUS-Feature_Image-1-768x572.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/HAMPUS-Feature_Image-1-1024x762.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></p>
<p>Ørsted 花园公寓是个翻新项目。建筑团队 Tegnestuen LOKAL 将建筑原本面向街道的普通立面彻底改造，建造了一个新的社交空间。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1375955" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/LOKAL-1.jpg" alt="" width="955" height="1000" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/LOKAL-1.jpg 955w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/LOKAL-1-360x377.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/LOKAL-1-768x804.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 955px) 100vw, 955px" /></p>
<div class="editor-image-source">
<p>▲ 建筑原貌</p>
</div>
<p>设计团队在原本开放阳台的位置建立了一系列三角型玻璃小阳台，为每户住户都创造了半私人的休息平台。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1375957" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/HAMPUS-11-1.jpg" alt="" width="1000" height="750" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/HAMPUS-11-1.jpg 1000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/HAMPUS-11-1-360x270.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/HAMPUS-11-1-768x576.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" /></p>
<p>与此同时，可开合活动的玻璃板不仅能减少街道嘈杂的噪音，同时也可在秋冬天保持室内温暖。</p>